---
// FoundationCredibility.astro. Social-proof-by-track-record strip for a new
// platform where traditional social proof (logos, reviews) is thin.
// Kaldon is new software, but the 5-phase process behind it has been used
// to launch 150+ brands. This strip makes that track record load-bearing:
// the platform is new, the playbook is not.
//
// Placement: directly below ConnectedPlatforms on the home page, so a
// visitor scrolling past the integration logos immediately sees the
// credibility context for the claims that follow.
---

<section class="foundation-strip">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="foundation-inner">
      <!-- Track record stat -->
      <div class="foundation-stat">
        <span class="foundation-num">150+</span>
        <div class="foundation-stat-meta">
          <span class="foundation-stat-label">Brands launched</span>
          <span class="foundation-stat-sub">using this 5-phase process</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Separator -->
      <div class="foundation-sep" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Context copy -->
      <div class="foundation-context">
        <span class="kicker" style="color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 8px; display: inline-block;">Process. Proven. Productized.</span>
        <p class="foundation-body">
          Kaldon is new software. The playbook isn't. The same 5-phase process has taken sellers from zero to 6-, 7-, and 8-figure annual revenues. Now it's an AI platform, at <span class="foundation-emph">1 / 100th the cost and 1 / 50th the time</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .foundation-strip {
    padding: 36px 0;
    background: var(--void);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .foundation-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1px 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .foundation-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .foundation-sep { display: none; }
  }

  .foundation-stat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .foundation-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 68px);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .foundation-stat-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .foundation-stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--chalk);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .foundation-stat-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--ghost);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .foundation-sep {
    width: 1px;
    height: 72px;
    background: var(--hairline);
  }

  .foundation-context {
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .foundation-body {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ghost);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .foundation-emph {
    color: var(--chalk);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
